		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You call out to an ally, granting them a small piece of advice or encouragement, which empowers them to do their best. Alternatively, you offer a brief prayer for your own success.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><p>Your target must be able to hear and understand you.</p><ul><li><p>Target adds [[/r 1d4]] to the next skill or tool check they make. The spell then ends.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>A @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class.Item.SmG14gsqWBtqmcjt]{bard} using guidance on themselves might sing a short line to inspire themselves. Guidance can take many forms, and you should feel free to be creative with it.</em></p>",
